Russia RTS Stock-Index Futures Fall at Start of Trading

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-04-14T15:28:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/russia-rts-stock-index-futures-fall-at-start-of-trading.html
Russia ’s RTS stock-index futures
expiring in June fell 0.1 percent to 197,150 by 11:19 a.m. in
 New York .  OAO Gazprom, the natural-gas export monopoly, slipped 0.1
percent. Contracts on OAO Lukoil, the country’s second-biggest
oil producer, were little changed, while contracts on OAO
Sberbank, Russia’s largest lender, rose 0.1 percent.  The Market Vectors Russia ETF, a U.S.-traded fund that
holds Russian shares, fell 1.3 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
 hpavliva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
